title: Rank 3 Challenger Team Integral LF Top and Support
body:
Challenger Team Integral (Previously AnVaro) is seeking a new Top and Support. 
We're looking for experience and committed players who are willing to put in the hours and effort required to make it into the 2016 OPL.

If you wish to apply, please fill out the attached form and we will be in contact if we feel like you would be a match. 

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 
Thanks ! We're looking forward to hearing from you ~

replies.body: Would also be interested if you have a coach/analyst position open
